para.verbatim: :return: data directory tied to the user, e.g. ``%USERPROFILE%\\AppData\\Local\\$appauthor\\$appname`` (not roaming) or ``%USERPROFILE%\\AppData\\Roaming\\$appauthor\\$appname`` (roaming)
